These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
Hobby: singing, writing, skydiving, video-games
Sport: lacrosse, ice-hockey, golf, surfing
1. Hobby:skydiving is between Sport:golf and Sport:ice-hockey##2
2. Hobby:video-games is on the left or right of Sport:golf##3
3. Sport:golf is not to the left of Sport:golf##8
4. Sport:ice-hockey != Hobby:skydiving##6
5. Hobby:skydiving is somewhere to the right of Hobby:singing##5
6. Hobby:singing is on the right of Sport:lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | video-games  | singing | skydiving | writing  |
| Sport   | lacrosse | golf   | surfing  | ice-hockey |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
Food: eggplant, artichoke, carrot, cucumber
Job: manager, security-guard, chef, electrician
1. Job:electrician is not to the left of Job:electrician##8
2. Food:eggplant is somewhere to the right of Food:cucumber##5
3. Food:eggplant == Job:security-guard##1
4. Food:cucumber is between Food:eggplant and Food:artichoke##2
5. Food:artichoke is somewhere between Food:carrot and Job:manager##7
6. Job:chef is somewhere to the left of Food:artichoke##5
7. Job:manager is not to the left of Job:manager##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | carrot | artichoke          | cucumber | eggplant     |
| Job    | chef      | electrician | manager | security-guard |

