.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
Job: dancer, dressmaker, analyst, accountant
Movie-Genre: scientific, romance, musical, disaster
1. Movie-Genre:scientific is not to the left of Job:analyst##8
2. Movie-Genre:romance is on the far left##1
3. Job:dressmaker is on the right of Job:dancer##1
4. Job:dressmaker is in an even position##4
5. Job:accountant is on the far left or far right##3
6. Job:dancer is somewhere to the left of Movie-Genre:disaster##5
7. Job:accountant == Movie-Genre:musical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | dancer | dressmaker | analyst     | accountant |
| Movie-Genre   | romance    | disaster   | scientific | musical    |

