2. Sport:ice-hockey is not to the left of Sport:biathlon##8
3. Sport:golf is on the right of Music-Genre:salsa##1
4. Music-Genre:classical is not to the right of Sport:golf##8
5. Music-Genre:ambient == Sport:ice-hockey##1
6. Music-Genre:ambient is on the right of Sport:golf##1
7. Music-Genre:electronic is somewhere to the left of Music-Genre:classical##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic   | salsa         | classical   | ambient    |
| Sport         | biathlon | water-polo | golf | ice-hockey |

