.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
Music-Genre: hip-hop, salsa, rock, gospel
Transport: motorbike, jet-ski, bike, skateboard
1. Music-Genre:hip-hop is between Music-Genre:gospel and Transport:motorbike##2
2. Transport:skateboard is on the far left##1
3. Transport:skateboard is on the left or right of Music-Genre:hip-hop##3
4. Music-Genre:salsa is somewhere to the right of Transport:motorbike##5
5. Transport:jet-ski == Transport:jet-ski##1
6. Music-Genre:rock != Transport:bike##6
7. Music-Genre:gospel is not to the right of Music-Genre:rock##8
8. Transport:motorbike is not to the left of Transport:jet-ski##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel   | hip-hop | rock | salsa |
| Transport     | skateboard | jet-ski       | motorbike  | bike    |

